name: :	Wiser Foods
overview: Incorporated in the year 2012, at New Delhi (India), we, “Wiser Foods” are recognized as prominent Importer, Distributor and Trader of optimum quality range of Basa Fish Fillet, Frozen Prawn, Frozen Chicken and Tilapia Fish.The offered products are procured from reliable vendors of the industry who ensure that these products are low in cholesterol, high in iron, protein, amino acids and free from any contamination. These frozen meat products are widely used to prepare no. of dishes and cuisines in homes, hotels, restaurants, etc. Our reliable vendors further process and safely pack these products to preserve the freshness and purity for a longer period under the supervision of food inspectors. Besides, these frozen meat products are highly appreciated among the clients for their delicious taste, purity, high nutritional value and longer shelf life. Further, our offered products are available in various packaging options at reasonable price range.
